cPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kgf1665703025767.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kgf1665703025767.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kgf1665703025767.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kgf1665703025767\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Subtype Field\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Subtype Field references a Supertype Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__section_wbj_1ll_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d964613e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__image_uwv_cll_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_field_modeled2_c84183a949a6608a6ed22baaba9f9402.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fld</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mmw1665703024582.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mmw1665703024582.html\" title=\"A Supertype Entity is an Entity that has one or more Subtype Entities.\">Supertype Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zhd1665702557352.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zhd1665702557352.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Modeled Entity.\">Modeled Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kgf1665703025767__table_d10517e1_d10518e1_d10519e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">SupertypeEntityName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">SubtypeEntityName</var>/fld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__section_odr_dll_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d964613e273\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__p_d95048e1_d95049e1_d95050e1\">A derived field specializes Modeled Field in the\n        following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__ul_svz_2ll_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__li_d37430e1_d37431e1_d37432e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__p_d95051e1_d95052e1_d95053e1\">It has a Subtype Entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__li_d37433e1_d37434e1_d37435e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kgf1665703025767__p_d95054e1_d95055e1_d95056e1\">If it is not derived from a Supertype Field, it must\n            be a Non-Database Field.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614111\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614111\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Subtype Field Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Subtype Field A Subtype Field references a Supertype Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: fld Main Development Object? No Part of: Supertype Entity Contains: Value, Property , Code Container Generalization: Modeled Field Specializations: — Compilation Output — URI format: ent: SupertypeEntityName /ent: SubtypeEntityName /fld: FieldName Specialization A derived field specializes Modeled Field in the following ways: It has a Subtype Entity as parent. If it is not derived from a Supertype Field, it must be a Non-Database Field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}